Class EOCSV

  • java.lang.Object
    • EOCSV

  • public class EOCSV
extends java.lang.Object
    This class supports 3 different export modes 1) All data from the database is exported 2) All data that specific facilitator are part off (by being part of an arrangement or an event). 3) All data from specific arrangements are exported. And 1 import mode
